heading_context: Donate and volunteer to aid humanitarian disasters
chunks.html_content: You can donate money to aid organisations and agencies, or volunteer your time and skills if there’s been a natural disaster or humanitarian emergency overseas.
chunks.plain_content:
Donate and volunteer to aid humanitarian disasters
You can donate money to aid organisations and agencies, or volunteer your time and skills if there’s been a natural disaster or humanitarian emergency overseas.

heading_context: Donate and volunteer to aid humanitarian disasters
chunks.html_content: Donate through the Disasters Emergency Committee (DEC). This will make sure your donation reaches those most in need.
chunks.plain_content:
Donate and volunteer to aid humanitarian disasters
Donations
Donate through the Disasters Emergency Committee (DEC). This will make sure your donation reaches those most in need.

heading_context: Donate and volunteer to aid humanitarian disasters
chunks.html_content: Do not send food or clothing directly to an affected area, because you could delay supplies reaching those most in need.
chunks.plain_content:
Donate and volunteer to aid humanitarian disasters
Donations
Do not send food or clothing directly to an affected area, because you could delay supplies reaching those most in need.

heading_context: Donate and volunteer to aid humanitarian disasters
chunks.html_content:
You can help by volunteering to:

  • organise a fundraising event
  • staff a phone line for an aid agency
  • work in a charity shop
chunks.plain_content:
Donate and volunteer to aid humanitarian disasters
Volunteering
In the UK
You can help by volunteering to:

  organise a fundraising event
  staff a phone line for an aid agency
  work in a charity shop

heading_context: Donate and volunteer to aid humanitarian disasters
chunks.html_content:
You can register with a disaster relief charity such as RedR if you have specific skills that can help, for example:

  • engineering
  • health
  • child protection
  • logistics
  • search and rescue
chunks.plain_content:

  logistics
  search and rescue

heading_context: Donate and volunteer to aid humanitarian disasters
chunks.html_content: Do not travel to a disaster-affected area unless you’re working with an aid agency.
